(111, 'A0BE', '英語會話與閱讀(下)：中階班', 'GR', '王靜嫻', 'A', 'B01-103', 45, NULL, 2, 1, '2', 45, '114', 'A', '1.依學生英文能力分級(分級名單公告於中心網頁_最新消息) 2.請同學於選課期間內依分級自行上網選課', '必', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '一', '5,6', '11,07,03', '如因疫情需線上上課請用googlemeet:連結如下https://meet.google.com/htf-efmi-urj1) developlearners’ fourlanguageskills: listening, speaking, readingandwriting, mainlyfocusedonlisteningandspeaking2) introducelearnerstoawiderangeofthemesincontemporaryworld3) motivatelearnerstothinkcriticallyabouttheissuesaddressedinthecourse4) guidelearnerstoreflectontheissuesandrelatetotheirownlifeexperiences'),
(112, 'A0BF', '英語會話與閱讀(下)：中階班', 'GR', '歐素雯', 'A', 'B01-108', 45, NULL, 2, 1, '2', 45, '114', 'A', '1.依學生英文能力分級(分級名單公告於中心網頁_最新消息) 2.請同學於選課期間內依分級自行上網選課', '必', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '三', '5,6', '10,04,11', 'TobuildtheconfidenceincommunicatinginEnglishToreinforcethestudents\' abilityinreadingandboosttheirmotivationinlearning'),
